:    \"description\" : \"HikariCP is a high-performance JDBC connection pool for Java applications. It manages database connections efficiently to reduce latency and resource overhead.\",\nmetadata/ch.qos.logback/logback-classic/1.4.1/reachability-metadata.json:926:  \"resources\": [\nmetadata/com.zaxxer/HikariCP-java7/2.4.13/reachability-metadata.json:226:  \"resources\" : [\nmetadata/org.liquibase/liquibase-core/4.27.0/reachability-metadata.json:6947:  \"resources\": [\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-common/1.19.0/reachability-metadata.json:2:  \"resources\": [\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-common/1.19.0/reachability-metadata.json:5:        \"typeReached\": \"io.opentelemetry.sdk.resources.Resource\"\nmetadata/com.zaxxer/HikariCP-java7/index.json:10:    \"description\": \"HikariCP is a high-performance JDBC connection pool for Java applications. It manages database connections efficiently to reduce latency and resource overhead.\",\nmetadata/dev.zio/zio-config-typesafe_3/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"ZIO Config Typesafe is a Scala 3 integration module that lets ZIO Config load HOCON data through the Typesafe Config library. It provides ConfigProvider helpers for resources, files, strings, and existing com.typesafe.config.Config values so ZIO applications can use Typesafe-backed configuration sources.\",\nmetadata/ch.qos.logback/logback-classic/1.5.7/reachability-metadata.json:1253:  \"resources\": [\nmetadata/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-sdk-common/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"OpenTelemetry SDK Common provides shared SDK support classes for Java telemetry implementations, including resources, instrumentation scope information, clocks, and asynchronous export result handling. It is used by other OpenTelemetry Java SDK modules to represent common metadata and utility behavior consistently across traces, metrics, logs, and exporters.\",\nmetadata/org.liquibase/liquibase-core/4.17.0/reachability-metadata.json:1206:  \"resou